---
title: Sweet Peach BBQ Bacon Burger with Roasted Carrot & Arugula Salad
description: We’re going back to school with this burger! First up, math. Peach + BBQ + Bacon = Insanely amazing. Next, science. Did you know salt is a natural flavor enhancer? That’s why BBQ sauce, roasted onion, and sizzly bacon combine perfectly with caramelized peaches to create flavor layering that lights up your taste buds. And for even more salty-sweet satisfaction, arugula is tossed on the side with roasted carrots, almonds, pickled onion, and a savory Dijon dressing. Yep, this A+ dinner is best in class.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-peach-bbq-bacon-burger-7a21c559.jpg
